data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom, 2-story home! With a 2 car garage, you will have plenty of space for your vehicles and belongings. This home has been fully remodeled to create a contemporary and stylish living space that is ready for you to move in and make your own. Step inside and be greeted by an open and airy living area with brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the first level. The spacious living room flows seamlessly into the all-new kitchen, which boasts stainless steel appliances and stunning granite countertops. The perfect space for hosting dinner parties and gatherings with friends and family. As you make your way upstairs, you will be greeted by three spacious and airy bedrooms, each featuring plush new carpeting that provides comfort and warmth underfoot. The primary bedroom boasts a walk in closet.  The full bathroom upstairs has been remodeled complete with new tile flooring, sleek shower surround, stylish vanity, and new toilet creating a luxurious atmosphere, perfect for indulging in pampering and relaxation.  The outside of the home is just as impressive as the interior, with a fenced-in backyard and patio, perfect for entertaining and relaxation. This home is located in a great neighborhood and is in close proximity to schools, parks, shopping, and entertainment. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a completely remodeled home in a fantastic location. Schedule a tour today!
